data.description: Large and Charming 4 Bedroom / 1 Bathroom with endless potential. Main floor features large living and dining rooms, hardwood living room, and hardwood dining room, and full eat-in kitchen. Upper floor features 4 good sized bedroom and large bathroom. The home is close to shopping and public transportation. Come see for yourself and you wont be disappointed. Property is perfect for savvy investor, or owner occupant. To report any concerns with a listing broker/agent or to report any property condition or other concern needing escalation, please call: 1-877-617-5274.
